        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'Open the deck above in PowerPoint for Web. Use Copilot in PowerPoint to add a 4-slide REIT-trustee annex covering Distribution Outlook, NAV Bridge, Covenant Headroom, and Distribution Decision Tree. Reference /file PROP_02_REIT_Distribution_Policy.docx and /file PROP_06_Lender_Covenant_Schedule.xlsx. Use the Designer pane to apply a consistent visual style and add a NAV bridge waterfall on the second annex slide.'},
