        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'Prepare a stakeholder communication map for an SLA breach across three anchor e-commerce contracts, a fleet utilisation drop, the APAD tachograph notice, and an upcoming peak campaign. Identify the priority audiences, the message each audience needs, the timing window, and the main communication risk if the message is mishandled. Present as a RAG table with Red for same-day audiences (the three breached anchors, APAD), Amber for 24-hour audiences (top-10 enterprise B2B, lead lender) and Green for monitor-only audiences.'}
