        {'instr':'Open `m365.cloud.microsoft/chat` > Agents > **Researcher** > select **Critique Mode**. Paste the prompt below — Researcher will self-critique each source and flag any claim it cannot independently verify.', 'prompt':'Research how listed integrated logistics and 3PL groups in Malaysia, Singapore, Indonesia and Thailand have responded to anchor e-commerce SLA breaches, fleet utilisation drops below 75%, and regulator compliance notices between 2022 and 2025. For at least 3 published case studies, identify the trigger event, the operations response within 30 days, and the customer and regulator outcome 12 months later. Critically, instruct Researcher to self-critique each source, verify every claim against the original disclosure or trade press, and flag any claim it cannot independently verify. Cite every source with publication date.'},
