        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'Upload LOG_04_Contract_Pipeline.xlsx to Analyst. Cross-reference the Anchor Contract Health, Service-Credit Triggers AND Renewal Schedule tabs to identify which anchor contracts are at greatest renewal risk, the cumulative service-credit exposure in MYR millions, and whether the deterioration accelerated in the last 6 weeks. Quantify the contribution of on-time, damage rate, and missed pickup KPIs, then build a waterfall chart for each at-risk anchor showing Opening SLA Score → On-Time → Damage → Missed Pickup → Closing SLA Score. Present a structured RAG table with columns for Anchor Contract, Main Driver, 6-Week Change, Renewal Risk and Recommended Action, and embed the 3 waterfall charts beneath it.'},
